HEADWORD: malt whisky
<hw>malt whisky</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>A whiskey distilled in Scotland (esp. whiskey made from malted
barley in a pot still); Scotch whisky.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Scotch, Scotch-whiskey, Scotch whisky.</syn>⟦br⟧
